name: Time. (Undersans886)
description:
Play through many hard levels.  This is an unforgiving game with no save points.  You mess up, you restart all the way back.  Good luck beating it.

! Instructions in game !

!All music by me !

! Keep in mind that this was made using the scratch engine, so there are bound to be bugs (and I'm also just a bad scripter).  If something weird happens, reload the page and it should be fixed, if not tell me in the comments so I can try and fix it !
